t with the standard cosmological model at\n2$\\sigma$ confidence level. Therefore, RM results can be used to constrain\ncosmological models in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Mar 2019 19:52:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Mar 2019 11:54:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 7 Sep 2019 10:58:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-09"}
